Summary: silver object moving erratically then disappearing.
divs: Sighting DetailsWatching the shy, noticing all the airplanes having no con trails today. After the fifth airplane, flying west to east, I see an object flying west to east but in an irregular pattern, it was fluttering like a butterfly. Then, it tales off gaining altitude, in a nne. direction and it disappeared very quickly. I was wondering if anyone else might have seen this?
